Day 5: Branch Management and Conflict Resolution 

Topics: 

Working with branches 

Merging branches 

Resolving merge conflicts 

Exercises: 

Merge a Branch: 

Add a file called feature.txt in feature-branch. 

Stage and commit the file. 

Switch to the main branch and merge feature-branch into it. 

Resolve a Merge Conflict: 

Modify README.md in both the main branch and feature-branch with different changes. 

Commit changes in both branches. 

Merge feature-branch into the main branch and resolve the conflict. 
